            <h2>What this policy covers</h2>
            <p>Bigup Web ("Bigup Web") respects and values your privacy. That's why Bigup Web has established this Privacy Policy (referred to as the "Privacy Policy" herein) - so that Bigup Web can disclose what information Bigup Web collects about you and how Bigup Web use, store and disclose such information. Bigup Web want to help you make an informed decision about whether or not to share your information with Bigup Web.</p>
